OL,6,FCouncillors have vowed to provide
OL,7,F"much-needed investment" to a number
OL,8,Fof care homes that were at risk of
OL,9,Fclosure.
OL,11,FLancashire County Council launched a
OL,12,Fconsultation in late 2025 over the
OL,13,Fproposed closure of five care homes
OL,14,Fand five day centres after the
OL,15,Fbuildings were deemed to be in a
OL,16,F"significantly poor condition".
