OL,6,FThe Reform-led council has now
OL,7,Fconfirmed the care homes will instead
OL,8,Freceive investment to "ensure
OL,9,Fcontinued stability and comfort for
OL,10,Fresidents, their families, and the
OL,11,Fstaff who support them".
OL,13,FCounty Councillor Graham Dalton and
OL,14,FAdult Social Care, said: "Our priority
OL,15,Fhas always been ` and remains ` doing
OL,16,Fwhat is right for the people of
OL,17,FLancashire who rely on our care.
