OL,6,F"That's why our review into the model
OL,7,Fof care across Lancashire has
OL,8,Fidentified that investment is long
OL,9,Fover due. Lancashire residents expect
OL,10,Fand deserve high-quality social care
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,F"We're committed to innovation and
OL,14,Finvestment that ensures services
OL,15,Fremain safe, sustainable and fit for
OL,16,Fthe future. Our existing care homes
OL,17,Fmust receive the investment they
OL,18,Fdeserve."
