OL,6,FThe decision comes after the council's
OL,7,Fconsultation received more than 1,600
OL,8,Fresponses, with many workers,
OL,9,Fresidents, and families voicing their
OL,10,Fworries about the prospect of the
OL,11,Fhomes closing.
OL,13,FHowever, the statement makes no
OL,14,Fmention of the five day centres that
OL,15,Fwere also part of the consultation
OL,16,Fmeaning their future remains in doubt.
