OL,6,FIn a statement, the council
OL,7,Facknowledged the distress the
OL,8,Fproposals have caused and vowed to set
OL,9,Fout the next steps to secure the
OL,10,Ffuture of the care homes at a cabinet
OL,11,Fmeeting.
OL,13,FCllr Dalton said: "Residents should be
OL,14,Fin no doubt that our administration is
OL,15,Fthinking of families and the workforce
OL,16,Fwhen we make decisions.
