OL,13,Fend of a contentious issue for the
OL,14,FReform-led council, with the proposed
OL,15,Fclosures leading to protests in
OL,16,FPreston on Saturday 17 January and
OL,17,Fwarnings of potential strike action if
OL,18,Fthe care homes closed.
