OL,6,FAt the protest, Julie Lindley read a
OL,7,Fstatement written by her 94-year-old
OL,8,Fmother, Annie, a resident of Grove
OL,9,FHouse in Adlington, who suffers from
OL,10,Fdementia and has mobility issues.
OL,12,FShe said: "I came to Grove House two
OL,13,Fyears ago, upset and confused, but I
OL,14,Fsoon settled in and made lots of new
OL,15,Ffriends .
OL,17,F"Some days I remember their names and
OL,18,Fsome days I don't, but who cares? We
OL,19,Fare all in the same boat together.
